European Credit Hires Allstate’s Montague as Financial Analyst

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 
2011-08-22T09:16:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/european-credit-hires-allstate-s-montague-as-financial-analyst.html
European Credit Management Ltd. ,
which manages 10 billion euros ($14 billion), said it hired
Robert Montague as a senior financial analyst.  Montague joined from Allstate Investment Management Co.,
where he was a senior credit analyst covering European banks.  London-based Montague will also help European Credit
Management to set up a new financials fund, according to a
statement from the company.  The appointment completes the build-out of European Credit
Management’s financials team, which also includes Satish Pulle
and Andy Li as portfolio managers, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Kuo in London at 
